      "paragraph_box_xyxy": [
        18,
        54,
        570,
        195
      ],
      "text": "\n[Greek Premier Karamanlis] [intends to press Tito at their meeting on 2 March for a definite yes or no on revival of the Balkan Pact]",
      "expanded_crop_box_xyxy": [
        0,
        40,
        594,
